    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NIGHTSHIFT</h2><br>Feel the retro vibes of the ‘80s with the colorful experience of NIGHTSHIFT - an 8-bit visual and playable arcade experience! Make your way on the highway, collect all the cassettes, boost your speed and reach Synthecity!<br><br>Our hero NIGHTSHIFT has to bring important documents to the extraction point. Will he reach Synthecity before it's too late?<br><br>You’re NIGHTSHIFT - a special agent of the secret services on a mission: <br><br>Make your way on the highway crowded with palms, neon buildings and bisons!<br><br>On your way you’ll have to sharp your senses to avoid all the obstacles, jump over incoming cars, stay away from the traffic and look out for roadworks!<br><br>Do you like to collect stuff? Grab all the cassettes! Hidden deviations will lead you to the ‘80s Gold cassette!<br><br><i>With the soundtrack DLC you can download the NIGHTSHIFT OST as well as more synthwave tracks of Robin Bressani.</i>",
